Help on skill: moving rock
Skill type: special
Usage duration: automatic

This skill allows you to imitate a tumbling rock to attack
aggressively against dangerous axe wielders, thus gaining 
the upper hand.

This skill is a part of the martial artists way of combat.
Your skill percent affects how well this skill works.
You need this kata when fighting unarmed against enemy with
some axe. This is the second kata.

